<br>
Good places to hunt is Tenebrous Mountains &amp; Scarlet Desert.  Collect up Bricks &amp; Blocks of Acrylia and Windstones (Windstones are the important part).<br>
<br>
Then see if you can't find a skill 200+ Smith to make some Acrylia Plate for you.  The Boots are AC 15, BP is AC 30 and Greaves are AC 20... plus some minor saves &amp; stats.<br>
<br>
Windstones are the real bottleneck on Acrylia Plate smithing, so if you can gather a bunch, you should have Smiths falling all over each other to help you out. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
P.S. I can't really recomend Human Cultural for you...  Mith Marr Imbue requires Diamonds, and Full Plate requires Royal Tempers (which are needed for the new Heraldic Plate).  If you get your hands on some Diamonds cheap, then the first thing you'll want is a Golden Idol of Mithaniel Marr.  After that, maybe an Imbued Field Breastplate. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showPrevMessage?topicID=1036.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showNextMessage?topicID=1036.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1036.topic&index=4><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.emailToFriend?topicID=1036.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.threadControl?topicID=1036.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1036.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1036.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpad